><a data-faro-user-action-name=\"header.nav.services\" href=\"/services\">Services</a><a data-faro-user-action-name=\"header.nav.financial-literacy\" href=\"/financial-literacy\">Financial Literacy</a><a data-faro-user-action-name=\"header.nav.book\" href=\"/book\">Book</a><a data-faro-user-action-name=\"header.nav.insights\" href=\"/blogs\">Insights</a><a data-faro-user-action-name=\"header.nav.gallery\" href=\"/gallery\">Gallery</a><a data-faro-user-action-name=\"header.nav.contact\" href=\"/contact\">Contact</a></nav><div class=\"header-actions\"><button class=\"language-button\" aria-label=\"Switch language to मराठी\" data-faro-user-action-name=\"header.language.toggle\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"15\" height=\"15\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-languages\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"m5 8 6 6\"></path><path d=\"m4 14 6-6 2-3\"></path><path d=\"M2 5h12\"></path><path d=\"M7 2h1\"></path><path d=\"m22 22-5-10-5 10\"></path><path d=\"M14 18h6\"></path></svg><span>मराठी</span></button><a data-faro-user-action-name=\"header.cta.contact\" class=\"button button-primary button-sm desktop-cta\" href=\"/contact\">Let’s talk<!-- --> <span aria-hidden=\"true\">↗</span></a><button class=\"menu-button\" aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-label=\"Open navigation\" data-faro-user-action-name=\"header.mobile-menu.open\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-menu\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M4 12h16\"></path><path d=\"M4 18h16\"></path><path d=\"M4 6h16\"></path></svg></button></div></div></header><main id=\"top\" class=\"\"><div class=\"scroll-progress\" style=\"transform:scaleX(0)\"></div><section class=\"hero\"><div class=\"hero-glow\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></div><div class=\"hero-grid container\"><div class=\"hero-copy\"><div class=\"eyebrow\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(12px)\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"14\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-sparkles\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M9.937 15.5A2 2 0 0 0 8.5 14.063l-6.135-1.582a.5.5 0 0 1 0-.962L8.5 9.936A2 2 0 0 0 9.937 8.5l1.582-6.135a.5.5 0 0 1 .963 0L14.063 8.5A2 2 0 0 0 15.5 9.937l6.135 1.581a.5.5 0 0 1 0 .964L15.5 14.063a2 2 0 0 0-1.437 1.437l-1.582 6.135a.5.5 0 0 1-.963 0z\"></path><path d=\"M20 3v4\"></path><path d=\"M22 5h-4\"></path><path d=\"M4 17v2\"></path><path d=\"M5 18H3\"></path></svg>Financial literacy • Distribution • Protection</div><h1 style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(24px)\">Build a wiser<br/><em>financial life.</em></h1><p class=\"hero-body\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(18px)\">Finopia helps families understand money, build financial discipline and make informed decisions—with education at the centre of every conversation.</p><div class=\"hero-actions\" style=\"opacity:0\"><a data-faro-user-action-name=\"home.hero.explore-approach\" class=\"button button-primary button-default\" href=\"/about\">Explore our approach<svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"17\" height=\"17\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-arrow-right\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M5 12h14\"></path><path d=\"m12 5 7 7-7 7\"></path></svg></a><a data-faro-user-action-name=\"home.hero.discover-book\" class=\"button button-secondary button-default\" href=\"/book\">Discover the book</a></div><div class=\"founder-strip\" style=\"opacity:0\"><div class=\"founder-monogram\" aria-hidden=\"true\">YK</div><div><span>Led by</span><strong>Yogesh Kadam CFP®</strong><small>CFP® Professional · Author · Financial Literacy Educator</small></div></div></div><div class=\"hero-visual\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:scale(0.96)\"><div class=\"hero-floor\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></div><div class=\"hero-scene\" style=\"transform:none\"><div class=\"orbit orbit-one\"></div><div class=\"orbit orbit-two\"></div><div class=\"scene-shadow\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></div><div class=\"wisdom-card\"><div class=\"wisdom-card-top\"><span>FINOPIA</span><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-badge-check\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M3.85 8.62a4 4 0 0 1 4.78-4.77 4 4 0 0 1 6.74 0 4 4 0 0 1 4.78 4.78 4 4 0 0 1 0 6.74 4 4 0 0 1-4.77 4.78 4 4 0 0 1-6.75 0 4 4 0 0 1-4.78-4.77 4 4 0 0 1 0-6.76Z\"></path><path d=\"m9 12 2 2 4-4\"></path></svg></div><div class=\"wisdom-orb\"><img alt=\"\" width=\"160\" height=\"160\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"1\" class=\"wisdom-orb-logo\" style=\"color:transparent\" sizes=\"112px\" srcSet=\"/_next/image?url=%2Fmedia%2Ffinopia-symbol.jpg&amp;w=16&amp;q=75 16w, /_next/image?url=%2Fmedia%2Ffinopia-symbol.jpg&amp;w=32&amp;q=75 32w, /_next/image?url=%2Fmedia%2Ffinopia-symbol.jpg&amp;w=48&amp;q=75 48w, /_next/image?url=%2Fmedia%2Ffinopia-symbol.jpg&amp;w=64&amp;q=75 64w, /_next/image?url=%2Fmedia%2Ffinopia-symbol.jpg&amp;w=96&amp;q=75 96w, /_next/image?url=%2Fmedia%2Ffinopia-symbol.jpg&amp;w=128&amp;q=75 128w, /_next/image?url=%2Fmedia%2Ffinopia-symbol.jpg&amp;w=256&amp;q=75 256w, /_next/image?url=%2Fmedia%2Ffinopia-symbol.jpg&amp;w=384&amp;q=75 384w, /_next/image?url=%2Fmedia%2Ffinopia-symbol.jpg&amp;w=640&amp;q=75 640w, /_next/image?url=%2Fmedia%2Ffinopia-symbol.jpg&amp;w=750&amp;q=75 750w, /_next/image?url=%2Fmedia%2Ffinopia-symbol.jpg&amp;w=828&amp;q=75 828w, /_next/image?url=%2Fmedia%2Ffinopia-symbol.jpg&amp;w=1080&amp;q=75 1080w, /_next/image?url=%2Fmedia%2Ffinopia-symbol.jpg&amp;w=1200&amp;q=75 1200w, /_next/image?url=%2Fmedia%2Ffinopia-symbol.jpg&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75 1920w, /_next/image?url=%2Fmedia%2Ffinopia-symbol.jpg&amp;w=2048&amp;q=75 2048w, /_next/image?url=%2Fmedia%2Ffinopia-symbol.jpg&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75 3840w\" src=\"/_next/image?url=%2Fmedia%2Ffinopia-symbol.jpg&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75\"/></div><div><small>Our philosophy</small><h2>Clarity before action.</h2><p>Because informed families make stronger decisions.</p></div><div class=\"wisdom-bars\"><i></i><i></i><i></i><i></i><i></i></div></div><div class=\"float-stat stat-one\"><strong>13+</strong><span>Years of experience</span></div><div class=\"float-stat stat-two\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"19\" height=\"19\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-graduation-cap\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M21.42 10.922a1 1 0 0 0-.019-1.838L12.83 5.18a2 2 0 0 0-1.66 0L2.6 9.08a1 1 0 0 0 0 1.832l8.57 3.908a2 2 0 0 0 1.66 0z\"></path><path d=\"M22 10v6\"></path><path d=\"M6 12.5V16a6 3 0 0 0 12 0v-3.5\"></path></svg><span><strong>CFP®</strong> <!-- -->Professional</span></div><div class=\"float-stat stat-three\"><strong>10K</strong><span>Families · Mission</span></div></div></div></div><div class=\"trust-rail container\"><span>Registered &amp; transparent</span><strong>ARN-337302</strong><i></i><strong>E641374</strong><i></i><strong>CFP® #<!-- -->126010</strong></div></section><section class=\"section founder-section\"><div class=\"founder-grid container\"><div class=\"portrait-placeholder portrait-photo\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(24px)\"><img alt=\"Yogesh Kadam CFP®\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"fill\" style=\"position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;color:transparent\" sizes=\"(max-width: 780px) 100vw, 420px\" srcSet=\"/_next/image?url=%2Fmedia%2Fyogesh-kadam-founder.png&amp;w=640&amp;q=75 640w, /_next/image?url=%2Fmedia%2Fyogesh-kadam-founder.png&amp;w=750&amp;q=75 750w, /_next/image?url=%2Fmedia%2Fyogesh-kadam-founder.png&amp;w=828&amp;q=75 828w, /_next/image?url=%2Fmedia%2Fyogesh-kadam-founder.png&amp;w=1080&amp;q=75 1080w, /_next/image?url=%2Fmedia%2Fyogesh-kadam-founder.png&amp;w=1200&amp;q=75 1200w, /_next/image?url=%2Fmedia%2Fyogesh-kadam-founder.png&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75 1920w, /_next/image?url=%2Fmedia%2Fyogesh-kadam-founder.png&amp;w=2048&amp;q=75 2048w, /_next/image?url=%2Fmedia%2Fyogesh-kadam-founder.png&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75 3840w\" src=\"/_next/image?url=%2Fmedia%2Fyogesh-kadam-founder.png&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75\"/><div class=\"portrait-caption\"><small>Founder · Finopia Services</small><strong>Yogesh Kadam CFP®</strong></div></div><div class=\"founder-copy\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(24px)\"><span class=\"kicker\">Meet the founder</span><h2>Financial education, with a human voice.</h2><p>For over 13 years, Yogesh Kadam CFP® has worked at the intersection of financial services and education. His purpose is simple: help families replace uncertainty with understanding.</p><blockquote>“<!-- -->Financial literacy is not about knowing everything. It is about asking the right questions before making a decision.<!-- -->”</blockquote><div class=\"credential-row\"><span><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-badge-check\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M3.85 8.62a4 4 0 0 1 4.78-4.77 4 4 0 0 1 6.74 0 4 4 0 0 1 4.78 4.78 4 4 0 0 1 0 6.74 4 4 0 0 1-4.77 4.78 4 4 0 0 1-6.75 0 4 4 0 0 1-4.78-4.77 4 4 0 0 1 0-6.76Z\"></path><path d=\"m9 12 2 2 4-4\"></path></svg>CFP® <!-- -->Professional</span><span><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-book-open\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M12 7v14\"></path><path d=\"M3 18a1 1 0 0 1-1-1V4a1 1 0 0 1 1-1h5a4 4 0 0 1 4 4 4 4 0 0 1 4-4h5a1 1 0 0 1 1 1v13a1 1 0 0 1-1 1h-6a3 3 0 0 0-3 3 3 3 0 0 0-3-3z\"></path></svg>Author</span><span><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-users-round\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M18 21a8 8 0 0 0-16 0\"></path><circle cx=\"10\" cy=\"8\" r=\"5\"></circle><path d=\"M22 20c0-3.37-2-6.5-4-8a5 5 0 0 0-.45-8.3\"></path></svg>Educator</span></div><a class=\"text-link\" data-faro-user-action-name=\"home.founder.journey\" href=\"/founder\">Read Yogesh’s story<svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-arrow-right\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M5 12h14\"></path><path d=\"m12 5 7 7-7 7\"></path></svg></a></div></div></section><section class=\"section services-section\"><div class=\"container\"><div class=\"section-heading split-heading\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(24px)\"><div><span class=\"kicker\">What we do</span><h2>One thoughtful ecosystem for your family’s financial life.</h2></div><p>Education, distribution and protection—connected by clear conversations and responsible guidance.</p></div><div class=\"service-grid\"><div class=\"service-card\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(24px)\"><div class=\"service-icon\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"22\" height=\"22\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-chart-no-axes-combined\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M12 16v5\"></path><path d=\"M16 14v7\"></path><path d=\"M20 10v11\"></path><path d=\"m22 3-8.646 8.646a.5.5 0 0 1-.708 0L9.354 8.354a.5.5 0 0 0-.707 0L2 15\"></path><path d=\"M4 18v3\"></path><path d=\"M8 14v7\"></path></svg></div><span>0<!-- -->1</span><h3>Mutual Fund Distribution</h3><p>Help selecting and accessing suitable mutual fund products with clear, process-led support.</p><a aria-label=\"Learn about Mutual Fund Distribution\" data-faro-user-action-name=\"home.service-card.mutual-fund-distribution\" href=\"/services\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"18\" height=\"18\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-arrow-right\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M5 12h14\"></path><path d=\"m12 5 7 7-7 7\"></path></svg></a></div><div class=\"service-card\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(24px)\"><div class=\"service-icon\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"22\" height=\"22\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-shield-check\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M20 13c0 5-3.5 7.5-7.66 8.95a1 1 0 0 1-.67-.01C7.5 20.5 4 18 4 13V6a1 1 0 0 1 1-1c2 0 4.5-1.2 6.24-2.72a1.17 1.17 0 0 1 1.52 0C14.51 3.81 17 5 19 5a1 1 0 0 1 1 1z\"></path><path d=\"m9 12 2 2 4-4\"></path></svg></div><span>0<!-- -->2</span><h3>Life Insurance Solutions</h3><p>Protection-focused solutions designed around responsibilities, dependants and life stages.</p><a aria-label=\"Learn about Life Insurance Solutions\" data-faro-user-action-name=\"home.service-card.life-insurance-solutions\" href=\"/services\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"18\" height=\"18\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-arrow-right\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M5 12h14\"></path><path d=\"m12 5 7 7-7 7\"></path></svg></a></div><div class=\"service-card\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(24px)\"><div class=\"service-icon\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"22\" height=\"22\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-heart-pulse\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M19 14c1.49-1.46 3-3.21 3-5.5A5.5 5.5 0 0 0 16.5 3c-1.76 0-3 .5-4.5 2-1.5-1.5-2.74-2-4.5-2A5.5 5.5 0 0 0 2 8.5c0 2.3 1.5 4.05 3 5.5l7 7Z\"></path><path d=\"M3.22 12H9.5l.5-1 2 4.5 2-7 1.5 3.5h5.27\"></path></svg></div><span>0<!-- -->3</span><h3>Health Insurance Solutions</h3><p>Guidance to understand health cover, exclusions and the importance of preparedness.</p><a aria-label=\"Learn about Health Insurance Solutions\" data-faro-user-action-name=\"home.service-card.health-insurance-solutions\" href=\"/services\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"18\" height=\"18\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-arrow-right\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M5 12h14\"></path><path d=\"m12 5 7 7-7 7\"></path></svg></a></div><div class=\"service-card\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(24px)\"><div class=\"service-icon\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"22\" height=\"22\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-book-open\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M12 7v14\"></path><path d=\"M3 18a1 1 0 0 1-1-1V4a1 1 0 0 1 1-1h5a4 4 0 0 1 4 4 4 4 0 0 1 4-4h5a1 1 0 0 1 1 1v13a1 1 0 0 1-1 1h-6a3 3 0 0 0-3 3 3 3 0 0 0-3-3z\"></path></svg></div><span>0<!-- -->4</span><h3>Financial Literacy Programs</h3><p>Practical learning experiences that turn financial concepts into everyday habits.</p><a aria-label=\"Learn about Financial Literacy Programs\" data-faro-user-action-name=\"home.service-card.financial-literacy-programs\" href=\"/services\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"18\" height=\"18\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-arrow-right\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M5 12h14\"></path><path d=\"m12 5 7 7-7 7\"></path></svg></a></div><div class=\"service-card\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(24px)\"><div class=\"service-icon\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"22\" height=\"22\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-users-round\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M18 21a8 8 0 0 0-16 0\"></path><circle cx=\"10\" cy=\"8\" r=\"5\"></circle><path d=\"M22 20c0-3.37-2-6.5-4-8a5 5 0 0 0-.45-8.3\"></path></svg></div><span>0<!-- -->5</span><h3>Investor Awareness Programs</h3><p>Clear, compliant education that helps participants ask better financial questions.</p><a aria-label=\"Learn about Investor Awareness Programs\" data-faro-user-action-name=\"home.service-card.investor-awareness-programs\" href=\"/services\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"18\" height=\"18\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-arrow-right\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M5 12h14\"></path><path d=\"m12 5 7 7-7 7\"></path></svg></a></div><div class=\"service-card\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(24px)\"><div class=\"service-icon\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"22\" height=\"22\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-landmark\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M10 18v-7\"></path><path d=\"M11.12 2.198a2 2 0 0 1 1.76.006l7.866 3.847c.476.233.31.949-.22.949H3.474c-.53 0-.695-.716-.22-.949z\"></path><path d=\"M14 18v-7\"></path><path d=\"M18 18v-7\"></path><path d=\"M3 22h18\"></path><path d=\"M6 18v-7\"></path></svg></div><span>0<!-- -->6</span><h3>Family Financial Management</h3><p>Simple frameworks for household cash flow, protection, goals and shared decisions.</p><a aria-label=\"Learn about Family Financial Management\" data-faro-user-action-name=\"home.service-card.family-financial-management\" href=\"/services\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"18\" height=\"18\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-arrow-right\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M5 12h14\"></path><path d=\"m12 5 7 7-7 7\"></path></svg></a></div></div><div class=\"center-action\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(24px)\"><a data-faro-user-action-name=\"home.services.view-all\" class=\"button button-secondary button-default\" href=\"/services\">View all services<svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-arrow-right\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M5 12h14\"></path><path d=\"m12 5 7 7-7 7\"></path></svg></a></div></div></section><section class=\"book-section section\"><div class=\"book-grid container\"><div class=\"book-stage\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(24px)\"><div class=\"book-shadow\"></div><div class=\"book-object\"><div class=\"book-spine\">पैशाचे शहाणपण · योगेश कदम</div><div class=\"book-cover book-cover-real\"><img alt=\"पैशाचे शहाणपण book cover\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"fill\" style=\"position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;color:transparent\" sizes=\"(max-width: 780px) 210px, 290px\" srcSet=\"/_next/image?url=%2Fmedia%2Fpaishache-shahanpan-book-cover.jpg&amp;w=16&amp;q=75 16w, /_next/image?url=%2Fmedia%2Fpaishache-shahanpan-book-cover.jpg&amp;w=32&amp;q=75 32w, /_next/image?url=%2Fmedia%2Fpaishache-shahanpan-book-cover.jpg&amp;w=48&amp;q=75 48w, /_next/image?url=%2Fmedia%2Fpaishache-shahanpan-book-cover.jpg&amp;w=64&amp;q=75 64w, /_next/image?url=%2Fmedia%2Fpaishache-shahanpan-book-cover.jpg&amp;w=96&amp;q=75 96w, /_next/image?url=%2Fmedia%2Fpaishache-shahanpan-book-cover.jpg&amp;w=128&amp;q=75 128w, /_next/image?url=%2Fmedia%2Fpaishache-shahanpan-book-cover.jpg&amp;w=256&amp;q=75 256w, /_next/image?url=%2Fmedia%2Fpaishache-shahanpan-book-cover.jpg&amp;w=384&amp;q=75 384w, /_next/image?url=%2Fmedia%2Fpaishache-shahanpan-book-cover.jpg&amp;w=640&amp;q=75 640w, /_next/image?url=%2Fmedia%2Fpaishache-shahanpan-book-cover.jpg&amp;w=750&amp;q=75 750w, /_next/image?url=%2Fmedia%2Fpaishache-shahanpan-book-cover.jpg&amp;w=828&amp;q=75 828w, /_next/image?url=%2Fmedia%2Fpaishache-shahanpan-book-cover.jpg&amp;w=1080&amp;q=75 1080w, /_next/image?url=%2Fmedia%2Fpaishache-shahanpan-book-cover.jpg&amp;w=1200&amp;q=75 1200w, /_next/image?url=%2Fmedia%2Fpaishache-shahanpan-book-cover.jpg&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75 1920w, /_next/image?url=%2Fmedia%2Fpaishache-shahanpan-book-cover.jpg&amp;w=2048&amp;q=75 2048w, /_next/image?url=%2Fmedia%2Fpaishache-shahanpan-book-cover.jpg&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75 3840w\" src=\"/_next/image?url=%2Fmedia%2Fpaishache-shahanpan-book-cover.jpg&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75\"/></div></div><div class=\"book-note\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"18\" height=\"18\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-book-open\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M12 7v14\"></path><path d=\"M3 18a1 1 0 0 1-1-1V4a1 1 0 0 1 1-1h5a4 4 0 0 1 4 4 4 4 0 0 1 4-4h5a1 1 0 0 1 1 1v13a1 1 0 0 1-1 1h-6a3 3 0 0 0-3 3 3 3 0 0 0-3-3z\"></path></svg><span>Written in Marathi<br/><strong>For every family</strong></span></div></div><div class=\"book-copy\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(24px)\"><span class=\"kicker light\">Featured publication</span><h2>पैशाचे शहाणपण</h2><h3>Money matters. Money wisdom matters more.</h3><p>A Marathi guide from financial literacy to financial independence—written to make complex ideas feel practical, familiar and useful.</p><ul><li><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-check\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M20 6 9 17l-5-5\"></path></svg>Everyday financial concepts</li><li><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-check\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M20 6 9 17l-5-5\"></path></svg>Written in simple Marathi</li><li><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-check\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M20 6 9 17l-5-5\"></path></svg>Built around better habits</li></ul><a data-faro-user-action-name=\"home.book.buy\" class=\"button button-primary button-default\" href=\"/book#buy\">Buy the book<svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"17\" height=\"17\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-arrow-right\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M5 12h14\"></path><path d=\"m12 5 7 7-7 7\"></path></svg></a></div></div></section><section class=\"proof-section section\"><div class=\"container\"><div class=\"section-heading split-heading\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(24px)\"><div><span class=\"kicker\">Trust, documented</span><h2>Credentials you can verify. Roles we state clearly.</h2></div><p>Professional qualifications and distributor registrations are presented openly—because trust begins with transparency.</p></div><div class=\"proof-grid\"><div class=\"proof-card\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(24px)\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-badge-check\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M3.85 8.62a4 4 0 0 1 4.78-4.77 4 4 0 0 1 6.74 0 4 4 0 0 1 4.78 4.78 4 4 0 0 1 0 6.74 4 4 0 0 1-4.77 4.78 4 4 0 0 1-6.75 0 4 4 0 0 1-4.78-4.77 4 4 0 0 1 0-6.76Z\"></path><path d=\"m9 12 2 2 4-4\"></path></svg><small>Professional credential</small><h3>CFP® <!-- -->Professional</h3><p>Certification number<!-- --> <!-- -->126010</p></div><div class=\"proof-card\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(24px)\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-file-check2 lucide-file-check-2\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M4 22h14a2 2 0 0 0 2-2V7l-5-5H6a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v4\"></path><path d=\"M14 2v4a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h4\"></path><path d=\"m3 15 2 2 4-4\"></path></svg><small>Mutual fund distribution</small><h3>ARN-337302</h3><p>EUIN <!-- -->E641374</p></div><div class=\"proof-card\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(24px)\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-shield-check\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M20 13c0 5-3.5 7.5-7.66 8.95a1 1 0 0 1-.67-.01C7.5 20.5 4 18 4 13V6a1 1 0 0 1 1-1c2 0 4.5-1.2 6.24-2.72a1.17 1.17 0 0 1 1.52 0C14.51 3.81 17 5 19 5a1 1 0 0 1 1 1z\"></path><path d=\"m9 12 2 2 4-4\"></path></svg><small>Insurance distribution</small><h3>HDFC Life</h3><p>Agency code<!-- --> <!-- -->HDF01946314</p></div></div></div></section><section class=\"community-section section\"><div class=\"container community-grid\"><div style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(24px)\"><span class=\"kicker light\">Community voices</span><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-quote\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M16 3a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v6a2 2 0 0 0 2 2 1 1 0 0 1 1 1v1a2 2 0 0 1-2 2 1 1 0 0 0-1 1v2a1 1 0 0 0 1 1 6 6 0 0 0 6-6V5a2 2 0 0 0-2-2z\"></path><path d=\"M5 3a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v6a2 2 0 0 0 2 2 1 1 0 0 1 1 1v1a2 2 0 0 1-2 2 1 1 0 0 0-1 1v2a1 1 0 0 0 1 1 6 6 0 0 0 6-6V5a2 2 0 0 0-2-2z\"></path></svg><blockquote>Financial education is most valuable when it changes the quality of a family’s next conversation.</blockquote><p>Verified client and reader testimonials will be published here with consent when the supplied media library is added.</p><a class=\"text-link light-link\" data-faro-user-action-name=\"home.community.testimonials\" href=\"/testimonials\">Explore testimonials<!-- --> <svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-arrow-right\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M5 12h14\"></path><path d=\"m12 5 7 7-7 7\"></path></svg></a></div><div class=\"gallery-preview home-launch-preview\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(24px)\"><a class=\"home-launch-photo p-0\" data-faro-user-action-name=\"home.gallery.preview.launch-photo.1\" href=\"/gallery\"><img alt=\"Book launch guests holding Paishache Shahanpan on stage\" loading=\"laz