ath d=\"m12 5 7 7-7 7\"></path></svg></a></div></div></section><section class=\"section insights-section\"><div class=\"container\"><div class=\"section-heading split-heading\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(24px)\"><div><span class=\"kicker\">Learn with Finopia</span><h2>Ideas for a calmer relationship with money.</h2></div><a class=\"text-link\" data-faro-user-action-name=\"home.insights.view-all\" href=\"/blogs\">View all insights<!-- --> <svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-arrow-right\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M5 12h14\"></path><path d=\"m12 5 7 7-7 7\"></path></svg></a></div><div class=\"article-grid\"><div class=\"article-card\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(24px)\"><a class=\"article-card-link\" data-faro-user-action-name=\"home.article.family-money-conversation\" href=\"/blogs/family-money-conversation\"><div class=\"article-art mint\"><span>0<!-- -->1</span><i></i><i></i><i></i></div><small>Money basics<!-- --> · <!-- -->6 min read</small><h3>The quiet power of a family money conversation</h3><p>A useful money conversation is not a lecture. It is a shared check-in about responsibilities, goals and the decisions that deserve clarity.</p><span class=\"text-link\">Read article<!-- --> <svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"15\" height=\"15\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-arrow-right\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M5 12h14\"></path><path d=\"m12 5 7 7-7 7\"></path></svg></span></a></div><div class=\"article-card\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(24px)\"><a class=\"article-card-link\" data-faro-user-action-name=\"home.article.small-financial-systems\" href=\"/blogs/small-financial-systems\"><div class=\"article-art blue\"><span>0<!-- -->2</span><i></i><i></i><i></i></div><small>Financial discipline<!-- --> · <!-- -->4 min read</small><h3>Small systems beat big financial resolutions</h3><p>Financial discipline rarely comes from a dramatic promise. It grows from simple systems that repeat even on ordinary busy days.</p><span class=\"text-link\">Read article<!-- --> <svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"15\" height=\"15\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-arrow-right\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M5 12h14\"></path><path d=\"m12 5 7 7-7 7\"></path></svg></span></a></div><div class=\"article-card\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(24px)\"><a class=\"article-card-link\" data-faro-user-action-name=\"home.article.protection-first-insurance\" href=\"/blogs/protection-first-insurance\"><div class=\"article-art sand\"><span>0<!-- -->3</span><i></i><i></i><i></i></div><small>Insurance literacy<!-- --> · <!-- -->7 min read</small><h3>Protection first: understanding what insurance is for</h3><p>Insurance becomes clearer when we see it first as protection for responsibilities, not as a shortcut for returns.</p><span class=\"text-link\">Read article<!-- --> <svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"15\" height=\"15\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-arrow-right\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M5 12h14\"></path><path d=\"m12 5 7 7-7 7\"></path></svg></span></a></div></div></div></section><section class=\"contact-band\"><div class=\"contact-band-inner container\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(24px)\"><div><span class=\"kicker light\">Begin with clarity</span><h2>A better financial conversation can start today.</h2><p>Tell us what you want to understand. We’ll help you find a clear next step.</p></div><div><a data-faro-user-ac